---
title: Cheeseburger Tacos with Special Sauce & Sesame Seeds
description: Enjoy your fast food with a twist  - these clever tacos pack the flavours of a classic cheeseburger into a handheld parcel that will surprise and delight you, right down to the special sauce and toasted sesame seeds that tie the whole meal together!
